HEADWORD: Bookmark
<hw>Book"mark`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something placed
in a book to guide in finding a particular page or passage; also, a
label in a book to designate the owner; a bookplate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bookmate</ent>⟦br⟧
